## Troubleshooting and Support

### Common Issues and Solutions

**Dashboard Loading Slowly:**
- **Symptom:** Dashboard takes >10 seconds to load
- **Solution:** Reduce time range or disable real-time updates
- **Prevention:** Optimize data queries and implement caching

**Missing Data Points:**
- **Symptom:** Gaps in performance metrics
- **Solution:** Check data collection system and restart if needed
- **Prevention:** Implement data validation and gap detection

**Alert False Positives:**
- **Symptom:** Too many non-critical alerts
- **Solution:** Adjust alert thresholds based on historical data
- **Prevention:** Implement alert suppression and correlation

**Inconsistent Metrics:**
- **Symptom:** Same metric shows different values in different views
- **Solution:** Synchronize metric calculations across dashboard components
- **Prevention:** Use centralized metric calculation services

